    bio: 'Kala Alexander is a North Shore Hawaiian surfer and notorious Pipeline enforcer known as a member of the Wolfpak, the group of local surfers who police the lineup at Pipeline. A powerful surfer in his own right with exceptional tube-riding ability, Alexander\'s reputation extends beyond surfing — his presence in the Pipeline lineup has been a defining feature of North Shore surf culture for decades.',
