    bio: "Brian Aragon is a Filipino-American professional aggressive inline skater from San Jose, California and one of the most stylish and technically skilled skaters in the sport's history. He is widely credited with helping define modern street inline skating through his film parts and competition performances. His smooth style and clean execution set a benchmark that influenced a generation of skaters.",
